            <div class="phone-note">
              <strong>Built to look polished on mobile.</strong>
              <p>
                Because most customers will see your business from Google, Instagram, or a link in bio first.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="builder-strip" aria-label="Built by Christian">
        <div class="container builder-card">
          <div class="builder-image">
            <img src="/images/christian-profile.jpg" alt="Christian Diaz, founder of Sites by Christian" />
          </div>

          <div class="builder-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">Built by Christian</p>
            <h2>Personal service from someone who understands small business.</h2>
            <p>
              You are not getting passed off to a random agency. Sites by Christian is led by
              Christian Diaz, a website builder and small business operator who understands design,
              customer flow, ecommerce, and the messy details behind running a real business.
            </p>
          </div>

          <a href="#about" class="builder-link">Meet Christian</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section dark-section">
        <div class="container solve-grid">
          <div class="dark-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow light">What we solve</p>
            <h2>Your website should make your business easier to understand.</h2>

            <p>
              A lot of small business websites start with good intentions, but the details get messy.
              Services are unclear, products are hard to manage, forms feel clunky, customers miss
              important information, and updates become one more thing the owner has to figure out.
            </p>

            <p>
              Sites by Christian focuses on both sides of the experience: the polished website your
              customers see and the practical structure behind it that helps your business stay organized.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="fit-card">
            <p class="eyebrow">Good fit</p>
            <h3>For businesses that need more than a pretty page.</h3>

            <div class="fit-list">
              {goodFit.map((item) => (
                <div class="fit-item">
                  <span></span>
                  <p>{item}</p>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section services-work-section" id="services-work">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head wide">
            <p class="eyebrow">Services & selected work</p>
            <h2>Choose the level that fits where your business is now.</h2>
            <p>
              Each tier is paired with a real project example so you can see how the work scales from
              a simple starter site to a more advanced ecommerce system.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-work-stack">
            {serviceProjects.map((service) => (
              <article class="service-work-card">
                <div class="service-info">
                  <p class="service-kicker">Service tier</p>
                  <div class="service-title-row">
                    <h3>{service.title}</h3>
                    <p class="price">{service.price}</p>
                  </div>

                  <p>{service.description}</p>

                  <a href="#contact" class="text-link">Start with this tier</a>
                </div>

                <div class="project-side">
                  <div class="project-preview-shell">
                    <div class="project-preview-top">
                      <span>Scrollable preview</span>
                      <span>↕</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-preview" tabindex="0" aria-label={`Scrollable preview of ${service.projectTitle}`}>
                      <img src={service.image} alt={service.imageAlt} loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="project-content">
                    <p class="project-type">{service.projectType}</p>
                    <h3>{service.projectTitle}</h3>
                    <p>{service.projectDescription}</p>

                    <div class="project-links">
                      {service.link ? (
                        <a href={service.link} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                          {service.linkLabel}
                        </a>
                      ) : (
                        <span>{service.linkLabel}</span>
                      )}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section support-section" id="pricing">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">Monthly support</p>
            <h2>Ongoing help for the updates you do not have time to manage.</h2>
            <p>
              Monthly plans are for business owners who want their website or store to stay current,
              organized, and supported after launch.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="support-grid">
            {supportPlans.map((plan) => (
              <article class="support-card">
                <div>
                  <h3>{plan.title}</h3>
                  <p>{plan.description}</p>
                </div>

                <p class="support-price">{plan.price}</p>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section about-section" id="about">
        <div class="container about-grid">
          <div class="portrait-card">
            <img src="/images/christian-profile.jpg" alt="Christian, founder of Sites by Christian" />
          </div>

          <div class="about-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">Meet Christian</p>
            <h2>Built by someone who understands the small business side, too.</h2>

            <p>
              Sites by Christian is led by Christian Diaz, a website builder and small business operator
              who understands that a website is not just a design project.
            </p>

            <p>
              A good site has to support real customers, real updates, real products, real services,
              and the day-to-day details that keep a business moving. The goal is to build websites
              that look clean, feel easy to use, and make the business easier to manage after launch.
            </p>

            <div class="about-points">
              <span>Personal service</span>
              <span>Entry sites</span>
              <span>Custom builds</span>
              <span>Ecommerce systems</span>
              <span>Operations-minded</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section guidance">
        <div class="container two-column">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow light">After launch</p>
            <h2>Clear guidance, not a confusing handoff.</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="rich-copy">
            <p>
              A finished website should not come with a “good luck” and no explanation. We provide
              guidance so you understand how your site is structured, what matters most, and where
              to go when something needs to change.
            </p>

            <p>
              For custom projects, we can create a personalized guide that explains your pages,
              products, forms, workflows, and common update steps in plain language.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section process-section" id="process">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">Process</p>
            <h2>A simple process with strong structure.</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="process-grid">
            {process.map((item) => (
              <article class="process-card">
                <span>{item.step}</span>
                <h3>{item.title}</h3>
                <p>{item.text}</p>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section faq-section" id="faq">
        <div class="container faq-grid">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
            <h2>A few things clients usually ask first.</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-list">
            {faqs.map((faq) => (
              <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>{faq.question}</summary>
                <p>{faq.answer}</p>
              </details>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section contact" id="contact">
        <div class="container contact-grid">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Start a project</p>
            <h2>Tell us what you are building.</h2>
            <p>
              Share a few details about your business, what kind of site you need, and when you are
              hoping to launch. We will use that to understand the right starting point.
            </p>
          </div>

          <form id="contact-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjkkykz" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New Sites by Christian inquiry" />

            <label class="honeypot">
              Leave this field empty
              <input type="text" name="_gotcha" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
            </label>

            <label>
              Name
              <input type="text" name="name" required />
            </label>

            <label>
              Business name
              <input type="text" name="business" />
            </label>

            <label>
              Email
              <input type="email" name="email" required />
            </label>

            <label>
              Phone number
              <input type="tel" name="phone" />
            </label>

            <label>
              Current website or social link
              <input type="text" name="current_site" />
            </label>

            <label>
              What do you need help with?
              <select name="service" required>
                <option value="">Select one</option>
                <option value="Entry Site">Entry Site</option>
                <option value="Custom Build">Custom Build</option>
                <option value="Ecommerce + Automations">Ecommerce + Automations</option>
                <option value="Monthly support">Monthly support</option>
                <option value="Not sure yet">Not sure yet</option>
              </select>
            </label>

            <label>
              Target launch timeframe
              <select name="launch_timeframe" required>
                <option value="">Select one</option>
                <option value="As soon as possible">As soon as possible</option>
                <option value="In the coming weeks">In the coming weeks</option>
                <option value="In the coming months">In the coming months</option>
                <option value="Closer to a year from now or more">Closer to a year from now or more</option>
                <option value="Not sure yet">Not sure yet</option>
              </select>
            </label>

            <label>
              Message
              <textarea name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
            </label>

            <button type="submit">Send inquiry</button>

            <p id="form-status" class="form-status" aria-live="polite"></p>

            <p class="form-note">We will review your inquiry and follow up by email.</p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <p>Sites by Christian</p>
        <span>Custom websites and ecommerce systems for small businesses.</span>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
      const form = document.getElementById("contact-form");
      const statusMessage = document.getElementById("form-status");

      if (form && statusMessage) {
        form.addEventListener("submit", async (event) => {
          event.preventDefault();

          const submitButton = form.querySelector("button[type='submit']");
          const formData = new FormData(form);

          statusMessage.className = "form-status";
          statusMessage.textContent = "";

          if (submitButton) {
            submitButton.disabled = true;
            submitButton.textContent = "Sending...";
          }

          try {
            const response = await fetch(form.action, {
              method: "POST",
              body: formData,
              headers: {
                Accept: "application/json",
              },
            });

            if (response.ok) {
              form.reset();

              statusMessage.textContent =
                "Thank you! Your inquiry was sent successfully. We will follow up by email soon.";
              statusMessage.className = "form-status success";
            } else {
              statusMessage.textContent =
                "Something went wrong. Please try again, or email us directly if the problem continues.";
              statusMessage.className = "form-status error";
            }
          } catch (error) {
            statusMessage.textContent =
              "Something went wrong. Please check your connection and try again.";
            statusMessage.className = "form-status error";
          } finally {
            if (submitButton) {
              submitButton.disabled = false;
              submitButton.textContent = "Send inquiry";
            }
          }
        });
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #fbf7ef;
    --soft: #f1eadf;
    --card: #ffffff;
    --text: #171717;
    --muted: #67615a;
    --border: #ddd4c8;
    --blue: #2563eb;
    --blue-dark: #173ea8;
    --blue-soft: #e6efff;
    --ink: #101828;
    --cream-card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
      sans-serif;
  }

  .container {
    width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 2rem));
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5.5vw, 4.9rem);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 660;
  }

  h2 {
    max-width: 760px;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.25rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    font-weight: 630;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 630;
  }

  .site-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 20;
    background: rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.9);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  }

  .nav-wrap {
    min-height: 72px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .brand {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  nav a:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .nav-cta {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 650;
  }

  .mobile-nav-cta {
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 38px;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--blue);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    font-weight: 750;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .mobile-section-menu {
    display: none;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 5.75rem 0 3rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08), transparent 22rem),
      var(--bg);
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(340px, 0.95fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 750;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  }

  .eyebrow.light {
    color: #93c5fd;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 650px;
    font-size: 1.12rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .button,
  button {
    min-height: 44px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 650;
  }

  .primary,
  button {
    background: var(--blue);
    color: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--blue);
  }

  .secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  button:disabled {
    cursor: not-allowed;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .trust-row,
  .about-points {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .trust-row span,
  .about-points span {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 0.45rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--blue-soft);
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 650;
  }

  .phone-showcase {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    justify-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    min-height: 680px;
  }

  .phone-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: min(100%, 360px);
    height: 690px;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 3rem;
    background:
      linear-gradient(145deg, #111827, #020617),
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18), transparent 12rem);
    box-shadow:
      0 30px 80px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.26),
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }

  .phone-speaker {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.15rem;
    left: 50%;
    z-index: 3;
    width: 96px;
    height: 24px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #020617;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .phone-screen {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 2.25rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .phone-screen::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: inherit;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), transparent 10rem),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16), transparent 5rem);
  }

  .phone-site {
    --scroll-distance: -38%;
    min-height: 1060px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.18), transparent 14rem),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fbfcff 58%, #f1eadf 100%);
    animation: phoneScroll 14s ease-in-out infinite;
    will-change: transform;
  }

  @keyframes phoneScroll {
    0%,
    14% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    50%,
    64% {
      transform: translateY(var(--scroll-distance));
    }

    100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .phone-hero {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 3.8rem 1.05rem 1.2rem;
  }

  .phone-site-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .phone-site-nav strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .phone-site-nav span {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--blue-soft);
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .phone-eyebrow,
  .phone-section-label {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .phone-hero h2 {
    font-size: 2.15rem;
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .phone-hero p {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .phone-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .phone-actions span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 34px;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .phone-actions span:first-child {
    background: var(--blue);
    color: white;
  }

  .phone-actions span:last-child {
    background: white;
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .phone-section {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.05rem;
  }

  .phone-mini-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .phone-mini-grid div {
    display: grid;
    align-content: end;
    min-height: 128px;
    padding: 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .phone-mini-grid span {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 0.8rem;
    background: var(--blue-soft);
  }

  .phone-mini-grid p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .phone-mini-grid strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .phone-feature {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    margin: 0.35rem 1.05rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 1.15rem;
    background: var(--ink);
  }

  .phone-feature p:first-child {
    color: #93c5fd;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .phone-feature h3 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.03;
  }

  .phone-feature p:last-child {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .phone-info-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .phone-info-list div {
    padding: 0.85rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
  }

  .phone-info-list strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .phone-info-list p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .phone-cta {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 0.35rem 1.05rem 1.2rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 1.15rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.16);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
  }

  .phone-cta p {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .phone-cta span {
    display: inline-flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--blue);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .phone-note {
    width: min(100%, 390px);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    border-radius: 1.1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
  }

  .phone-note strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .phone-note p {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .builder-strip {
    padding: 0 0 4.5rem;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .builder-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.14);
    border-radius: 1.35rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
  }

  .builder-image {
    width: 116px;
    height: 116px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1.35rem;
    background: var(--soft);
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
  }

  .builder-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 62%;
  }

  .builder-copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .builder-copy h2 {
    max-width: 760px;
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2vw, 1.85rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
  }

  .builder-copy p:last-child {
    max-width: 820px;
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .builder-link,
  .text-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: fit-content;
    min-height: 40px;
    padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--blue-soft);
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 750;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .text-link {
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 5.25rem 0;
  }

  .dark-section,
  .guidance {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.28), transparent 24rem),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #101828, #0b1220);
  }

  .solve-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .dark-copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .dark-copy h2,
  .guidance h2 {
    color: white;
  }

  .dark-copy p,
  .guidance p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
  }

  .fit-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    padding: 1.35rem;
    border-radius: 1.35rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
  }

  .fit-card h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 2.4vw, 2.1rem);
  }

  .fit-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .fit-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 14px 1fr;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(241, 234, 223, 0.72);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .fit-item span {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    margin-top: 0.45rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .services-work-section {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1), transparent 24rem),
      var(--soft);
  }

  .section-head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .section-head.wide {
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .service-work-stack {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.35rem;
  }

  .service-work-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.82fr) minmax(0, 1.18fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: stretch;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 1.45rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
  }

  .service-info {
    display: grid;
    align-content: start;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .service-kicker,
  .project-type {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 750;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .service-title-row {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .service-title-row h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 3vw, 2.45rem);
  }

  .price {
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-weight: 800;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .project-side {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1.2rem;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
  }

  .project-preview-shell {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .project-preview-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }

  .project-preview-top span:first-child {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 750;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .project-preview-top span:last-child {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 1.65rem;
    height: 1.65rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
  }

  .project-preview {
    height: 330px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    overscroll-behavior: contain;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), rgba(241, 245, 249, 0.7)),
      #f8fafc;
  }

  .project-preview:focus {
    outline: 3px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
    outline-offset: -3px;
  }

  .project-preview img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .project-preview::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 0.55rem;
  }

  .project-preview::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: #eef2f7;
  }

  .project-preview::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .project-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
  }

  .project-links a,
  .project-links span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 34px;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--blue-soft);
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .project-links a:hover,
  .text-link:hover,
  .builder-link:hover {
    background: var(--blue);
    color: white;
  }

  .support-section {
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .support-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .support-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    justify-content: space-between;
    min-height: 260px;
    padding: 1.35rem;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.06);
  }

  .support-card div {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .support-price {
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .about-section {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12), transparent 22rem),
      var(--soft);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .portrait-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 540px;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.14);
    background: var(--soft);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.1);
  }

  .portrait-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 540px;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
  }

  .about-copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    border-radius: 1.35rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
  }

  .two-column,
  .contact-grid,
  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .rich-copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 740px;
  }

  .process-section {
    background: var(--soft);
  }

  .process-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .process-card {
    padding: 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.05);
  }

  .process-card span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 750;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .process-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
  }

  .faq-section,
  .contact {
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .faq-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 34px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 650;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  form {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--card);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.06);
  }

  label {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 550;
  }

  input,
  select,
  textarea {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 0.95rem;
    background: white;
    color: var(--text);
    font: inherit;
  }

  textarea {
    resize: vertical;
  }

  button {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .form-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .form-status {
    display: none;
    margin-top: -0.2rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 0.95rem;
    border-radius: 0.85rem;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 650;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .form-status.success {
    display: block;
    background: #dcfce7;
    color: #166534;
    border: 1px solid #86efac;
  }

  .form-status.error {
    display: block;
    background: #fee2e2;
    color: #991b1b;
    border: 1px solid #fecaca;
  }

  .honeypot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -9999px;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  footer {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  footer p {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  footer span {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .service-work-card,
    .solve-grid,
    .support-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .project-preview {
      height: 390px;
    }

    .support-card {
      min-height: auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav {
      display: none;
    }

    .mobile-nav-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
    }

    .mobile-section-menu {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }

    .mobile-section-menu::-webkit-scrollbar {
